184
00:15:36,820 --> 00:15:38,560
peninggalan kuno
yang tersembunyi di dalamnya.

185
00:15:39,230 --> 00:15:41,780
Eliksir kuno, senjata sakti,

186
00:15:41,780 --> 00:15:44,350
